===============================================================================
THE BRUTAL TRUTH
===============================================================================

BASE CASE ECONOMICS (No Policy Support):
  Cost:     $223/tCO2
  Revenue:  $100/tCO2 (carbon $50 + materials $35 + ecosystem $15)
  Margin:   -$123/tCO2 (UNPROFITABLE)

This framework does NOT work without at least one of:
  □ IRA 45Q tax credit ($130/tCO2) - requires EPA MRV approval
  □ Premium carbon buyers ($75+ per tCO2) - Microsoft, Stripe, Shopify tier
  □ Farm Bill CRP payments ($100-200/acre/year) - stacked with carbon credits
  □ Major cost reductions (50%+) through R&D breakthroughs

OPTIMISTIC SCENARIO (Scale + Premium Markets):
  Cost:     $179/tCO2 (economies of scale)
  Revenue:  $145/tCO2 (premium markets + IRA 45Q partial)
  Margin:   -$34/tCO2 (STILL UNPROFITABLE)

Even the optimistic case barely breaks even. This is NOT a slam-dunk business.

